  <h1>COVID-19 Guide for Kids!</h1>
  <p><i>As the world enters an unknown future, the children of healthcare workers are at their most vulnerable. These kids must understand the complexities of COVID-19 and its relationship with the healthcare worker(s) in their family. Have the child of the healthcare worker explore this site!  </i> <p>
  <img src="https://uknow.uky.edu/sites/default/files/styles/uknow_story_image/public/GettyImages-1207650868.jpg" alt="Child wearing face mask" width="450" height="300">

