      <h3 style="text-align:center" >The Situation</h3>
      <p style="text-align:center">Everything is different now. Summer break started months earlier than usual. You don't eat dinner at restaurants or hang out with your friends as often as you used to. Your parent(s) might be working until late at their medical center. The phrases "COVID-19" and "Coronavirus" are always being used in your house. What's going on might seem very confusing, but today you will go on an interactive journey to understand the situation at hand. Start by watching the video below, then take a look at the image below to see how the spread of COVID can be reduced with social distancing and quarantine!    
      </p>
      <iframe width="350" height="250" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GoXxmzKdick" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen> </iframe>
