      <p style="text-align:center">
      As a child of a healthcare worker, remember to keep in mind how important the role of your parent is during this wild time. They might not be around as much because their ability to help people is needed now more than ever. It's natural to be scared for them. Your parent must feel just as scared as you feel. Try to talk out your emotions with them. One of the best things you can do for your parent is to keep clean and free of germs so that you can reduce their worry! Click on the video below to learn how you can be safe during this pandemic!
      <p>
          </p>
       <iframe width="350" height="250" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/arN3ZfxcNf4?start=13" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>

